text: haey trong chea mcheasa del ban pongreab phendei haey trong ban bangkeut phnom cheachraen( chea lomnung) ning t ne l cheachraen now leu vea( phendei) haey trong kaban bangkeut now leu vea nouv real phleanouphl teangoasa aoy mean chea kou trong thveu aoy peloyb krobadandab pelothngai . pitabrakd nasa teangoasa noh kuchea phosdo tang samreab krom del cheh pichearna
